    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M/G\">C7M/G</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Deixa que minha mão errante adentre atrás</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Na frente</span>\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Em cima, em baixo, entre</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Minha América, minha terra à vista</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Reino de paz se um homem só a conquista</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Minha mina preciosa, meu império</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cº\">Cº</span>                            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Feliz de quem penetre o teu mistério</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Liberto-me ficando teu escravo</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Onde cai minha mão, meu selo gravo</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nudez total: todo prazer provém do corpo</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">(Como a alma sem corpo) Sem vestes</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#\">G#</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Como encadernação vistosa</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Feita para iletrados, a mulher se enfeita</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#º\">D#º</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas ela é um livro místico e somente</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A alguns a que tal graça se consente</span>\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É dado lê-la</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fm\">Fm</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A#7\">A#7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu sou um, quem sabe... hummmm</span>\n",
